mixin interfood-logo()
	section.interfood-logo&attributes(attributes)
		.interfood-logo__container
			img(src="assets/img/coffee-beans.png" alt="coffee").interfood-logo__infinity
			p.interfood-logo__name Colorful Ethiopia
			p.interfood-logo__text
				| Website was designed as one of two applications for
				| exhibitions taking place in Ethiopia in year 2017.
				span.interfood-logo__lonebird Lonebird Creative Studio
				| was put in task to create a different non-stereotypical
				| look of Ethiopia, modern, peculiar, with rich potential.
				| We made entire story-telling concept and structure, also
				| having put special effort in content writing, we created image of
				| Ethiopia as an attractive platform for investing activities.
			img(src="assets/img/interfood-lap.png" alt="interfood-lap").interfood-logo__logo-big


